steps.name: Click on the 'Companies' button from the sidebar menu
Click on the 'Clients' tab from the 'Companies' page
Click on the client name from the table
Click on the 'Transactions' tab from the company landing page
Click on the '+Add transaction' from the 'Transactions' tab at the company landing page
Select the 2023 option from the 'Associated year' dropdown
Click on the 'Transaction type' dropdown field
Select the 'Renewal' option inside the 'Transaction type' dropdown field
Click on the 'Finish' button to complete the transaction creation
